[{"id":"VR876696","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A laser beam is incident on two closely-spaced, parallel slits that are a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"d\"><math alttext=\"d\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>d</mi></math></span></span> apart. An interference pattern is then formed on a screen that is a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"L\"><math alttext=\"L\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>L</mi></math></span></span> from the slits. Adjacent bright spots in the interference pattern are a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta s\"><math alttext=\"delta s\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>s</mi></math></span></span> apart, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta s is much less than L\"><math alttext=\"delta s is much less than L\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>s</mi><mo>≪</mo><mi>L</mi></math></span></span>. If the slits are replaced by different slits separated by a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction d over 3\"><math alttext=\"the fraction d over 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mi>d</mi><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math></span></span>, what is the new distance between adjacent bright spots in the resulting interference pattern formed on the same screen by the same laser?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR876696_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction delta s over 9 \"><math alttext=\"the fraction delta s over 9 \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction delta s over 3\"><math alttext=\"the fraction delta s over 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 delta s\"><math alttext=\"3 delta s\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>s</mi></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"9 delta s\"><math alttext=\"9 delta s\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mn>9</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>s</mi></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]